content.rendered:
The film focuses on the last day of the 23-day feast of the monster known from the previous parts. That’s when Sergeant Tubbs and his team decide to destroy the creature. The monster, on the other hand, does not intend to give up the fight. As the fight goes on, the team gets closer to the monster’s secret

Director: Victor Salva

Writer: Victor Salva

Stars: Stan Shaw. Gabrielle Haugh. Brandon Smith
